title: Christine: Original Motion Picture Soundtrack
description:
This is the complete original motion picture soundtrack for John Carpenter's Christine featuring all 15 songs used in the film as listed by IMDB.

Track Listing:

1. - Bad to the Bone - George Thorogood
2. - Not Fade Away - Buddy Holly and the Crickets
3. - Pledging My Love - Johnny Ace
4. - We Belong Together - Robert & Johnny
5. - Keep A-Knockin' - Little Richard
6. - I Wonder Why - Dion & the Belmonts
7. - Harlem Nocturne - The Viscounts
8. - Little Bitty Pretty One - Thurston Harris
9. - Beast of Burden - The Rolling Stones
10. - Come On, Let's Go - Ritchie Valens
11. - Bony Moronie - Larry Williams
12. - Not Fade Away - Tanya Tucker
13. - Runaway - Bonnie Raitt
14. - The Name of the Game - Abba
15. - Rock n' Roll is Here to Stay - Danny & the Juniors
